quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,62,"Haele ba kholoang ho se senotsoeng ho uena, le balatelang mangolo a Ma-Juda, Ba-Keresete le ma-Sabia – le bohle ba kholoang ho Allah le ho letsatsi la bofelo, le ba etsang ka ho loka – Ruri moputso oa bona o ho Mong`a bona, bake ke ba eba le ts’abo kapa eona mesarelo"
  2,63,"Hopolang re entse selekane le lona, re phahamisetsa tlhoro ea thaba Sinai ho ba kaholimo ho lona, Ra Re: “Tsitlallelang ka tieo ho seo re le nehileng sona, le be le hopole seo se fuperoeng ke eona, mohlaope le ts`abe `Mopi"
  2,64,"La koeneha le ka morao ho moo, hoja e se be ka lereko la Allah le mohau oa hae, le ka be le le ba tahlehong"
  2,65,"Etsoe le tseba hantle ka ba robileng sabata har’a lona, re ile ra re ho bona: “le be lits’oene, le tellehe le hona ho hlouoa!”"
  2,66,"Eaba re etsa sena hoba mohlala nakong ea bona, le ho tsoala ea bona; e bile e le thuto ho ba ts’abang Allah"
  2,67,"Hopolang hore Moshe o ile a re ho batho ba habo: “Allah U le laela ho etsa sehlabelo ka khomo,” ba araba ba re: “u re fetola lits`eisa?” Moshe a arabela: “Allah U nthuse ke se be har’a liphoqo!”"
  2,68,"Ba re: “re kopele ke hona ho Mong`a hau a ke a re hlakisetse hore na khongoana eo ke e joang!” Moshe a re: “U itse,”: Ruri ke khongoana e holileng ho lekana kapa e matlafetseng, empa e be lipakeng tsa maemo a mabeli a na; ka hona etsang kamoo le laeloang ka teng.”"
  2,69,"Ba re: “re kopele ho Mong`a hau a re hlakisetse ‘mala oa eona.” Moshe a arabela: “Ruri ke khongoana e ts’ehla ba litau. Ho phatsima ke ‘mala oa eona, e tle e thabise babohi.”"